Release Notes (v1.0.0)
HOL2 SaveGuard v1.0.0 — Initial Release
Automatic save backup and restore tool for High On Life 2.
Features:

Automatic backups every 10 minutes (configurable) with change detection
One-click restore with safety backup before overwriting
All save slots supported (Slot0, Slot1, Slot2)
Interactive menu — no code editing required
Portable — extract and run, no install needed
Locked file retry handling for mid-save safety
Configurable retention (max backups, max age)
Optional auto-start on Windows login

How to use:

Extract the zip anywhere
Double-click Launch_SaveGuard.bat
Press 1 to start monitoring
Play the game
Attach HOL2_SaveGuard_v1.0.zip as a release asset
